; 180754 ; 180757","2018-10-26T12:08:12.877Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/989497/answer","Biography information for Alok Sharma","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/989497/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/989497/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2018-10-17","Universal Credit","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, what assessment her Department has made of the potential effect on vulnerable claimants of the roll-out of universal credit under (a) current systems and (b) the managed migration process.","false","Biography information for Neil Gray","Airdrie and Shotts","Neil Gray","180753"
